ISLAND WIDE SECURITY<br>
 <br>
Hiring "Team Players" for Full and Part Time positions:<br>
<br>
<br>
Site Supervisor position for large Condominium in Down Town Starting $ 15.00<br>
<br>
<br>
Hiring Flex Security Officer's  $11.00 - $12.00<br>
Serves as utility position that will train at various client sites, serve as a back-up to other officers, and provide temporary and part-time site coverage. <br>
Be willing to work the 3 different shifts (day/swing/grave, etc) and sometimes 6 days per week as needed.<br>
Able to work on weekends and holidays with limited notice.<br>
Able to travel to and from different sites.<br>
<br>
<br>
All Other Site's Starting is $10.50 as of January 1, 2017<br>
<br>
Site Opening's :<br>
<br>
Waianae :  12hr shifts 0800-2000 or 2000-0800 Weekends<br>
<br>
Downtown :<br>
1-Day Shift 0700-1500 or 0800-1600<br>
4-Graves Shifts 2300-0700 <br>
3-Swing Shifts 1500-2300 or 1600-2400<br>
<br>
<br>
Applicants must be able to work weekends and holidays.  All shifts available. Paid training and uniform provided. Medical with Drug coverage. Applicants will be screened and the most qualified applicants will be asked to participate in the interview process.  <br>
<br>
JOB SITES:<br>
Waikiki<br>
DownTown<br>
Kalihi<br>
PearlCity<br>
Waipahu<br>
Waianae<br>
<br>
Qualifications/Requirements<br>
Guard Card Certification (Act 208) REQUIRED<br>
All applicants must possess a valid Hawaii State I.D / Drivers license.<br>
Must be able to Stand and Walk for long periods of time. <br>
Able to speak and write clearly the English language.<br>
Able to work under pressure; and keep calm in every different situation.<br>
High degree of integrity, initiative, and motivation <br>
Ability to do Multi-tasking and manage time efficiently <br>
Ability to exercise good judgment <br>
Must be able to work NIGHTS, WEEKENDS and HOLIDAYS! <br>
<br>
Valid State of Hawaii Guard Card is required<br>
Available positions start to immediately <br>
prior Military or active Military is a plus. <br>
<br>
Starting Pay :  $10.50 -to- $12.00<br>
 <br>
PLEASE EMAIL ME YOUR RESUME...<br>
Ron Padayhag <br>
rpadayhag_iws@yahoo.com<br>
<br>
CALL FOR APPOINTMENT:<br>
Monday-Friday  9:30am-2:30pm<br>
<br>
Island Wide Security<br>
1000 Bishop St.  Suite # 902<br>
Hon, Hi 96813<br>
Office # 737-3100<br>
Ron Padayhag <br>
rpadayhag_iws@yahoo.com<br>
<br>
